Exploring SAP Fiori 2.0 - An Award Winning UX for delightful customer experiences
August 09th, 2017 (Wednesday) from 01:00 PM to 01:30 PM EST
Register Now
 
WEBINARS Check out our Webinar Depot for latest updates | Check it Out!!
 
 
With the evolution of latest applications in SAP related solutions, a new technology has been set across on-premise and cloud solutions with a better user experience, called SAP Fiori 2.0. This design is a winner of the prestigious Red Dot Design Award in interaction category because of its significant step in the expansion of business applications along with a delightful new visual theme called Belize.
 
Want to learn more about the importance of Belize theme and how the app finder can be used to access user menu from backend applications in Fiori? Then, join us on August 09th, 2017 (Wednesday) at 01:00 PM EST as our experts will talk about the technical stack for implementing Fiori 2.0 and it's amazing features such as notifications area, accessing transactions in your user menu in ECC, app finder and the Me area. Also know the impact on Fiori 1.0 Apps and how to migrate them to Fiori 2.0.
